      "post_content": "I remember when I first started, my friend sported a Mirrodin White-Blue Artifact deck, and his deck's box art featured this guy. I was in such awe when I saw this.   \n  \nNow, after 6 years and nearly $500 sunk into the game, I can easily say that it is pretty average... at least it's a better drawback than [Rusted Sentinel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rusted Sentinel).",
